   "type": "text",
   "x": 108,
   "y": 420,
   "width": 677.22,
   "height": 16.25,
   "text": "Access-A egress order:  allow TCP 80/443  →  allow UDP 123 (NTP)  →  block remaining to External",
   "originalText": "Access-A egress order:  allow TCP 80/443  →  allow UDP 123 (NTP)  →  block remaining to External",
   "fontSize": 13,
   "fontFamily": 5,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 12
  },
  {
   "angle": 0,
   "strokeColor": "#757575",
   "backgroundColor": "transparent",
   "fillStyle": "solid",
   "strokeWidth": 2,
   "strokeStyle": "solid",
   "roughness": 1,
   "opacity": 100,
   "roundness": null,
   "seed": 10152,
   "version": 1,
   "versionNonce": 10153,
   "isDeleted": false,
   "groupIds": [],
   "frameId": null,
   "updated": 1,
   "boundElements": [],
   "link": null,
   "locked": false,
   "type": "text",
   "x": 60,
   "y": 468,
   "width": 1552.79,
   "height": 15,
   "text": "The gateway routes tagged VLANs down the switch trunk; each zone keeps its own subnet and hosts. Ordered Access-A rules permit only web and NTP egress before the catch-all block, so a rule placed out of order drops HTTPS and NTP together.",
   "originalText": "The gateway routes tagged VLANs down the switch trunk; each zone keeps its own subnet and hosts. Ordered Access-A rules permit only web and NTP egress before the catch-all block, so a rule placed out of order drops HTTPS and NTP together.",
   "fontSize": 12,
   "fontFamily": 5,
   "textAlign": "left",
   "verticalAlign": "top",
   "containerId": null,
   "lineHeight": 1.25,
   "baseline": 11
  }
